data.description: Under Construction. The beautiful Amelia plan by LGI Homes is located within the gorgeous community of The Ridge at Swan Lake. This new one-story home features an open floor plan, 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths complete with over $10,000 in upgrades including energy-efficient Whirlpool® kitchen appliances, spacious countertops, 36" upper cabinets with crown molding, brushed nickel hardware and an attached two-car garage. The Amelia encompasses a master suite complete with a walk-in closet, as well as a utility room, covered back patio and front yard landscaping. In addition, The Ridge at Swan Lake is just minutes away from Legoland and Disney World, and is walking distance from Lake Marie Park and Dundee Recreational Park.
